  "description": "<p>Job Highlights</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good development opportunities with growing Bedding specialist</li>\n  <li>5 mins walk from Tai Seng MRT</li>\n  <li>Immediate Hiring</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Scope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide a welcoming, patient, and pressure-free in-store experience</li>\n  <li>Follow up with potential customers’ post-visit</li>\n  <li>Liaise with customers on their orders and deliveries</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties when assigned by superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong ability to close deals</li>\n  <li>Resilient &amp; self-motivated attitude</li>\n  <li>Well-groomed &amp; professional image</li>\n  <li>Those with prior sales experience &amp; knowledge in bedding will have an added advantage.</li>\n</ul>",
